{
  "stem": "1479.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had in Poland, they had all kinds of collaborators.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Nazis found Poland an excellent ground to get help, as they were the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were Polish collaborators, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Ukrainians wore the black uniforms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You were numb.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were in such a shock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You did not know what's going on, because the next room was waiting another group of Nazis.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were spraying us with some kind of disinfectant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but we were numb.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Number one, the most scary thing was, you know, not realizing, because those were not-- they cannot comprehend.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You cannot imagine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You did not recognize your sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You looked so different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We looked not human.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We looked like creatures.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And finally, after the spraying, we were brought to the shower room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who can forget the sound when the steel doors closed, to the shower room?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we are packed in the shower room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody dared to take a breath, because all did-- we looked at the ceilings, looking at the vents and waiting for the Zyklon B to come down, the gasses.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did you know about that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, you already heard what was going on, what the shower rooms were, for what purpose.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We spent over there in the shower room a few anxious moment until, unexpectedly, they start the gas water came down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So for the first time, we took a deep breath, and again, with this sigh of relief and hoping, maybe we're gonna live another day and another day.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the feeling that we are saved for a-- for a short time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from there, we were brought-- from the shower room, we were brought to a barrack, in which there is no excuse for it.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
